What is Gold-Filled?

Gold-filled is an economical alternative to solid gold. By law, it has 1/20th by weight layer of 14 karat gold permanently bonded over a core of base metal. It is tarnish-resistant, safe for sensitive or allergic to sterling silver skin and unlike gold plate, it will not wear off. It is a great way to enjoy affordable gold jewelry.
